<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lego Collection</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar',{page:''}) %>
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="hero-content text-center">
            <div class="max-w-md">
              <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Greetings</h1>
              <p class="py-6">Explore the robot-themed Lego sets and other similar themes in Lego's unique approach to robotic styled sets that capture creativity and lifelike design</p>
              <a href="lego/sets">
                <button class="btn btn-primary">Begin Here</button>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
              <img class="w-full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/8557-1.jpg" alt="set 1" />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title">Exo-Toa</h2>
              <p>This set released in 2002 Internationally, with both arms possesing a unique function</p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                <a href="lego/sets/Jan-57">
                  <button class="btn btn-primary">More Info</button>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
              <img class="w-full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/8547-1.jpg" alt="set 2" />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title">Mindstorms NXT 2.0</h2>
              <p>The second set in the Mindstorms series was introduced at the Lego Shop in the US in 2009</p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                <a href="lego/sets/Jan-47">
                  <button class="btn btn-primary">More Info</button>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
              <img class="w-full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/8556-1.jpg" alt="Set 3" />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title">Boxor</h2>
              <p>Released in 2002 Internationally, pushing down on the set causes its arms to punch forward </p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                <a  href="lego/sets/Jan-56">
                  <button class="btn btn-primary">More Info</button>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
</body>
</html>